==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:3-->
The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet CreateSheet]]}} tool adds a new spreadsheet object to the active document, which will be opened in a new tab in the [[main_view_area|main view area]].

==Usage== <!--T:4-->

<!--T:5-->
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet CreateSheet]]}} button.
# Edit the contents of the cells.
# Close the spreadsheet tab when you are finished, the values are saved automatically as you type them.


